'''路易斯機械與工具公司'''（{{lang-en|Lewis Machine & Tools Company}}，簡稱LMT）是一家位於美國[[艾奥瓦州|愛荷華州]][[埃爾德里奇_(愛荷華州)|埃爾德里奇]]的輕兵器及[[抑制器|抑制器]]生產商。LMT的產品被[[美国|美國]]、[[英国|英國]]、[[新西兰|紐西蘭]]、[[爱沙尼亚|愛沙尼亞]]等國家的軍隊使用。由於2010年代起LMT獲得越來越多的國防訂單，因此在2016起開始同時使用LMT防務（{{lang-en|LMT Defense}}）為公司名稱。

LMT是美國少數仍一手包辦全部生產工序，不依賴承包商的生產商，LMT現時擁有鍛造廠，以及CNC銑床、五軸銑床等設備<ref>{{Cite web|title=Lewis Machine & Tool Company {{!}} Custom Weapons Manufacturing|url=https://lmtdefense.com/custom-mfg/|accessdate=2021-02-10|author=|date=|format=|work=LMT|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124175502/https://lmtdefense.com/custom-mfg/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，機匣、槍管、零配件等皆為自行生產，而在引進[[线切割|線切割]]技術後扳機系統亦改為自行生產。另外LMT在埃爾德里奇的新廠區設有100碼射擊管，所有槍管皆會進行試射以保證精度。

== 歷史 ==
1976年，Karl Lewis在開始在[[傑納西奧_(伊利諾伊州)|傑納西奧]]的[[春田兵工廠|春田兵工廠]]工作，並因此學習了多種加工機具的操作方式。在得到上司的許可下，Karl Lewis在週末利用公司的機具製作各種零部件。後來，在市場上除役槍械的需求下，Karl Lewis開始生產槍機座，並離開了春田兵工廠<ref name=":7">{{Cite web|title=Sweat Lead And Steel - Karl Lewis|url=https://lmtdefense.com/sweat-lead-and-steel-karl-lewis/|accessdate=2021-02-09|date=2019-12-26|work=LMT|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121210329/https://lmtdefense.com/sweat-lead-and-steel-karl-lewis/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1980年，Karl Lewis在[[伊利诺伊州|伊利諾州]][[米蘭_(伊利諾伊州)|米蘭]]租用一家汽車店的角落成立了LMT<ref name=":7" />，公司目標為向美國軍警提供精密加工的高品質武器<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Our Story of Weapons Engineering|url=https://lmtdefense.com/our-story/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=|date=|format=|work=LMT|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203112023/https://lmtdefense.com/our-story/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2005年，LMT成為[[联邦总务署|聯邦總務署]]供應商，其產品可供應予全球超過30萬的聯邦人員<ref name=":0" />。

2009年，[[英國軍隊|英軍]]與其他國家的軍隊一樣在[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]遇上[[5.56×45mm_NATO|5.56 NATO]]步槍威力及射程不足的問題。因此在12月，[[英國國防部|英國國防部]]初步編列150萬[[英镑|英鎊]]作緊急作戰需求合約（{{Lang-en|Urgent Operational Requirements}}）的預算，以尋找一款7.62 NATO口徑，在500-800公尺能有效殺傷的步槍。LMT的LM308MWS在英軍的測試中擊敗了[[黑克勒-科赫|黑克勒-科赫]]的[[HK417自動步槍|HK417]]、[[埃斯塔勒国营工厂|FN]]的[[FN_SCAR突擊步槍|SCAR-H]]、Sabre Defence的XR-10、以及奈特軍械和Oberland Arms的產品，被採用為[[L129A1精確射手步槍|L129A1]]，並透過執法國際（{{Lang-en|Law Enforcement International}}）進口至英國<ref>{{Cite web|title=Taking Back The Infantry Half-km: Britains L129A1|url=http://www.defenseindustrydaily.com/Taking-Back-The-Infantry-Half-km-Britains-L129A1-06426/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=Defense Industry Daily staff|date=2010-06-08|last=|first=|format=|work=Defense Industry Daily|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330135722/https://www.defenseindustrydaily.com/Taking-Back-The-Infantry-Half-km-Britains-L129A1-06426/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Sharpshooter: The UK’s New L129A1 7.62x51mm Rifle|url=http://www.sadefensejournal.com/wp/sharpshooter-the-uks-new-l129a1-7-62x51mm-rifle/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=Dan Shea|date=2012-01-11|last=|format=|work=Small Arms Defense Journal|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210180805/http://www.sadefensejournal.com/wp/sharpshooter-the-uks-new-l129a1-7-62x51mm-rifle/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=The Lewis Machine & Tool Sharpshooter System – The All-American Commercial Model|url=https://www.ammoland.com/2012/04/the-lewis-machine-tool-sharpshooter-system/|accessdate=2021-02-07|date=2012-04-25|last=Riehl|first=F.|work=AmmoLand.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302075851/https://www.ammoland.com/2012/04/the-lewis-machine-tool-sharpshooter-system/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在獲得英國國防部合約的不久後，LMT獲得了來自丹麥的榴彈發射器合約。LMT因此推出了導軌安裝型的[[M203榴彈發射器|M203]]<ref name=":7" />。

2012年，英國交通警察局開始使用10.5英吋槍管的CQB Defender作為警員制式步槍<ref>{{Cite web|title=FOI Response 794-14 Firearms used by BTP|url=https://www.btp.police.uk/pdf/FOI%20Response%20794-14%20Firearms%20used%20by%20BTP.pdf|accessdate=2021-02-08|author=British Transport Police|date=|format=|publisher=|language=en-GB|archive-date=2015-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150919095257/http://www.btp.police.uk/pdf/FOI%20Response%20794-14%20Firearms%20used%20by%20BTP.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Guns on the Underground: Armed police to routinely patrol Tube amid threat from ISIS|url=https://www.express.co.uk/news/uk/612619/ISIS-armed-police-tube-London-Underground|accessdate=2021-02-07|date=2015-10-17|last=Austin|first=Jon|work=Express.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119063604/https://www.express.co.uk/news/uk/612619/ISIS-armed-police-tube-London-Underground|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年8月，[[紐西蘭國防軍|紐西蘭國防軍]]宣佈LMT的CQB MRP獲選為新的制式步槍<ref>{{Cite web|title=New Zealand Army Selects LMT To Replace Steyr AUG|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2015/08/18/new-zealand-army-selects-lmt-to-produce-rifle-to-replace-steyr-aug/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=Nathaniel F|date=2015-08-18|format=|work=The Firearm Blog|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224162559/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2015/08/18/new-zealand-army-selects-lmt-to-produce-rifle-to-replace-steyr-aug/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並共採購了9,040把步槍，合約總值5,900萬紐西蘭元。後來此批步槍出現撞針斷裂等問題，LMT在保固下免費為紐西蘭國防軍的全數步槍更換成「品質標準比美國軍方標準更高」的新撞針<ref>{{Cite web|title=NZDF's new rifles - all 9040 of them - get firing pin replacements after breakages|url=https://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/nzdfs-new-rifles-all-9040-of-them-get-firing-pin-replacements-after-breakages/CFH5YF6HYBRVXSH22PLBMNRLDA/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=David Fisher|date=2018-09-19|format=|work=NZ Herald|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214061214/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/nzdfs-new-rifles-all-9040-of-them-get-firing-pin-replacements-after-breakages/CFH5YF6HYBRVXSH22PLBMNRLDA/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=LMT Warranties Components with New Zealand Defense Forces MARS-L|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2018/09/25/lmt-replaces-components-under-warranty-with-new-zealand-defense-forces/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=Miles|date=2018-09-25|format=|work=The Firearm Blog|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114164008/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2018/09/25/lmt-replaces-components-under-warranty-with-new-zealand-defense-forces/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年12月，LMT的MARS-L／MARS-H在[[愛沙尼亞國防軍|愛沙尼亞國防軍]]的測試中擊敗了黑克勒-科赫的[[HK416突擊步槍|HK416 A5]]／HK417 A2及[[西格&紹爾|SIG Sauer]]的[[SIG_MCX突擊步槍|MCX]]／[[SIG_SG_716戰鬥步槍|SIG716G2 DMR]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Estonian Rifle Trials: SIG, H&K & LMT Rifles In Running|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2018/04/05/estonian-rifle-trials-sig-hk-lmt-rifles-in-running/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=Matthew Moss|date=2018-04-05|format=|work=The Firearm Blog|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118053045/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2018/04/05/estonian-rifle-trials-sig-hk-lmt-rifles-in-running/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref group="註">本來美國的愛國者軍械工廠（POF）的步槍亦獲選進入下一階段測試，但因步槍交付出現延誤而被排除</ref>，成為愛沙尼亞國防軍新的制式步槍。愛沙尼亞國防軍將採購16,000把步槍，合約總值2,200萬歐元<ref>{{Cite web|title=Lewis Machine & Tool Company wins automatic firearms contract|url=https://news.err.ee/882156/lewis-machine-tool-company-wins-automatic-firearms-contract|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=Aili Vahtla|date=2018-12-04|last=|first=|format=|work=ERR|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115190023/https://news.err.ee/882156/lewis-machine-tool-company-wins-automatic-firearms-contract|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由於來自愛沙尼亞的大額合約，LMT在2018年11月開始在埃爾德里奇興建新的設施<ref>{{Cite web|title=Lewis Machine & Tool Moving Production from Illinois to Iowa|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2019/02/04/lewis-machine-tool-moving-production-from-illinois-to-iowa/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=Matthew Moss|date=2019-02-04|format=|work=The Firearm Blog|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029074708/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2019/02/04/lewis-machine-tool-moving-production-from-illinois-to-iowa/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在2019年5月正式自米蘭遷至埃爾德里奇<ref>{{Cite web|title=LMT Defense Opens The New Facility in Eldridge, Iowa|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2019/05/24/lmt-defense-opens-a-new-facility-in-eldridge-iowa/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=Hrachya H|date=2019-05-24|format=|work=The Firearm Blog|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225203358/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2019/05/24/lmt-defense-opens-a-new-facility-in-eldridge-iowa/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。LMT指舊址的128個職位全數移至新址，並希望在當地創造50個新職位<ref>{{Cite web|title=Gun maker moving to Eldridge is bringing huge contract for Estonia|url=https://qctimes.com/news/local/gun-maker-moving-to-eldridge-is-bringing-huge-contract-for-estonia/article_e3a22f00-826c-5b2e-867f-9779c45f56f8.html|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=|date=2019-01-04|last=Ickes|first=Barb|format=|work=The Quad-City Times|publisher=|language=en}}</ref>。

由於愛沙尼亞的要求，LMT為其研發了新的歐洲式扳機系統，不論擊鎚狀態皆可將射擊選擇桿調至保險，並基於此推出了一系列新扳機。另外也與Visible Assets合作推出了位於握把內的射擊計數器，並可由軍械士以手持掃瞄器掃瞄射擊計數器，由系統自動判斷該槍的狀態<ref name=":6">{{Cite web|title=[TFB GUNFEST] LMT's Shot Counter Grip Module For Military And LE|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2021/01/18/lmts-shot-counter-grip/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=Doug E|date=2021-01-18|format=|work=The Firearm Blog|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119063927/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2021/01/18/lmts-shot-counter-grip/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

