== 產品特點 ==
LMT其中一系列最著名的產品是其一體式[[AR-15半自動步槍|AR-15]]及[[SR-25狙擊步槍|SR-25]]上機匣。此系列的特點為護木跟上機匣皆自同一[[7075鋁合金|7075 T6鋁]]鍛造件加工而成，因此頂部的導軌為一連續結構，在安裝瞄準鏡、夜視鏡等時無需擔心護木跟上機匣間存有公差而歸零不準。槍管以LMT專利的雙螺銷系統安裝，可以快速更換槍管以更換口徑、槍管長度，以及在直噴式氣動及短行程活塞間轉換。LMT指重新裝上曾經歸零的槍管時誤差應小於1 [[弧分|MOA]]<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=[TFB GUNFEST] New LMT Rifles, Uppers, and Triggers for 2021|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2021/01/31/tfb-gunfest-new-lmt-rifles-uppers-and-triggers-for-2021/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=James Reeves|date=2021-01-31|format=|work=The Firearm Blog|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227094900/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2021/01/31/tfb-gunfest-new-lmt-rifles-uppers-and-triggers-for-2021/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由於LMT持有一體式上機匣的專利，因此柯爾特及[[加拿大柯爾特|加拿大柯爾特]]分別推出其一體式上機匣時亦需向LMT申請及支付專利權費<ref>{{Cite web|title=FIRST LOOK: Colt Canada's C20 Sniper Rifle|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2019/09/26/first-look-colt-canadas-c20-sniper-rifle/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=Matthew Moss|date=2019-09-26|format=|work=The Firearm Blog|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120121727/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2019/09/26/first-look-colt-canadas-c20-sniper-rifle/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而同樣曾生產一體式上機匣的Mega Arms則因不願在法律程序耗費資源而決定轉而發展新的平臺<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mega Arms halts sale of monolithics; LMT granted patent|url=https://www.militarytimes.com/off-duty/gearscout/2012/07/19/mega-arms-halts-sale-of-monolithics-lmt-granted-patent/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=|date=2012-07-19|format=|work=Military Times|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021104022/https://www.militarytimes.com/off-duty/gearscout/2012/07/19/mega-arms-halts-sale-of-monolithics-lmt-granted-patent/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

